<div>
  <% unless user.veteran_status == :newbie %>
  <p>
    <b>Congratulations, your veteran status saves you money.</b>
  </p>

  <p>
    You are listed as a <%= user.veteran_title %>,
    which saves you <%= number_to_currency(user.vet_savings) %> on each
    FitnessCamp. Also, your veteran status enables you to pay by
    the session or establish a membership.
  </p>

  <% else %>

  <p>
    If you have completed a Fitness Camp before, you are eligible for
    discounts and other payment options.  However, our records show
    that this is your first camp. Please let us know if this is incorrect.
  </p>

  <% end %>
  <div style="clear:both;"></div>
</div>
<h3>You are registering for the following fitness camp<%= @cart.items.size > 1 ? "s" : "" %>:</h3>